Uses of Class
squidpony.squidmath.TableSet

  • Packages that use TableSet 
    Package Description
    squidpony.squidmath
    A very broad package containing random number generators, geometry tools, and some classes for combinatorics.

    • Uses of TableSet in squidpony.squidmath

      Methods in squidpony.squidmath that return TableSet 
      Modifier and Type Method and Description
      TableSet<C,R> TableSet.reorder(int... ordering)
      Given an array or varargs of replacement indices for this OrderedSet's iteration order, reorders this so the first item in the returned version is the same as getAt(ordering[0]) (with some care taken for negative or too-large indices), the second item in the returned version is the same as getAt(ordering[1]), etc.
      TableSet<C,R> TableSet.shuffle(RNG rng)
      Randomly alters the iteration order for this OrderedSet using the given RNG to shuffle.
      Constructors in squidpony.squidmath with parameters of type TableSet 
      Constructor and Description
      TableSet(TableSet<? extends C,? extends R> t)
      Creates a new hash set with DEFAULT_LOAD_FACTOR as load factor copying a given collection.
